<div class="card">
  <div class="card-header">
    <h4>SALIENT FEATURES OF THE PLAN</h4>
  </div>
  <div class="card-body">
    <h5 class="card-title">Plan Description</h5>
    <p class="card-text">
      This Group Basic Life Insurance Security System (GBLISS) insurance plan is designed to provide life and accident insurance to individual members of cooperatives.
    </p>
    <h5 class="card-title">Minimum Participation</h5>
    <p class="card-text">
      At least <b><%= gp.agreement.minimum_participation.humanize %> (<%= gp.agreement.minimum_participation %>)</b> eligible members shall be enrolled by the cooperative to implement this plan.
    </p>
    <h5 class="card-title">Eligibility</h5>
    <p class="card-text">
      <ol type="a">
        <li>
          at least (18) years of age but not over sixty-five (65) years old.
        </li>
        <li>
          in good health and physically able to to perform activities of daily living (ADLs) such as eating, bathing, dressing, toileting, transferring (walking), and self-control at the commencement date of this policy or of the coverage.
        </li>
        <li>
          an active member of the cooperative in good standing.
        </li>
        <li>
          a natural person and residing in the Philippines
        </li>
      </ol>
    </p>
    <h5 class="card-title">Benefit Provisions</h5>
    <p class="card-text">
      <table class="table">
        <thead>
          <th>Coverage</th>
          <th>Sum Insured</th>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <% gp.plan_unit.unit_benefits.each do |ub| %>
            <tr>
              <td><%= ub.benefit.name %></td>
              <td><%= to_currency(ub.coverage_amount) %></td>
            </tr>
          <% end %>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </p>
    <p class="card-text">
      <small><b>Note: AD & D, TPD, and HIB is only applicable to members age 18 to 65 years old. Renewal of members whose age is 66 to 69 years old will be covered only with Life and Burial Benefit</b></small>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>